('hcsr04', 'HC-SR04', 'Ultrasonic Distance Sensor', 'GPIO', '{"TRIG": "PA1", "ECHO": "PA8"}', 'Voltage divider on ECHO if using non-5V-tolerant pin', '5V sensor. ECHO pin outputs 5V — use 5V-tolerant pin or voltage divider. Range: 2-400cm.', 'HC-SR04 HCSR04 ultrasonic distance sonar range'),
('dht22', 'DHT22', 'Temperature/Humidity Sensor', 'GPIO', '{"DATA": "PA0"}', '10k pull-up resistor on data line', 'Single-wire protocol. Range: -40-80C, 0-100% RH. 3.3V or 5V compatible. Reads every 2 seconds max.', 'DHT22 AM2302 temperature humidity digital'),
('ws2812b', 'WS2812B', 'Addressable LED Strip', 'GPIO', '{"DATA": "PA0"}', '330-470 ohm resistor on data line, 1000uF capacitor on power', '5V LEDs but data line accepts 3.3V from most STM32 pins. Use timer DMA for precise timing. 60mA per LED at full white.', 'WS2812B WS2812 neopixel addressable LED RGB strip'),
('a4988', 'A4988', 'Stepper Motor Driver', 'GPIO', '{"STEP": "PA0", "DIR": "PA1", "ENABLE": "PA2"}', 'Separate motor power supply 8-35V', 'Connect STEP to timer pin for precise frequency control. MS1/MS2/MS3 for microstepping. Current limit set by potentiometer.', 'A4988 stepper motor driver NEMA step direction'),
('mcp4725', 'MCP4725', 'DAC (Digital-to-Analog Converter)', 'I2C', '{"SCL": "PB6", "SDA": "PB7"}', '4.7k pull-up resistors', 'I2C address: 0x60 or 0x62. 12-bit single channel DAC. Output 0-3.3V. STM32F103C8T6 has no built-in DAC — use this module.', 'MCP4725 DAC digital analog converter output voltage I2C'),
('pca9685', 'PCA9685', 'PWM/Servo Driver', 'I2C', '{"SCL": "PB6", "SDA": "PB7"}', '4.7k pull-up resistors, external power for servos', 'I2C address: 0x40-0x7F (configurable). 16 PWM channels at 12-bit resolution. Ideal for controlling many servos or LEDs. Separate V+ power for servos.', 'PCA9685 PWM servo driver 16 channel I2C'),
('ads1115', 'ADS1115', 'ADC (16-bit External)', 'I2C', '{"SCL": "PB6", "SDA": "PB7"}', '4.7k pull-up resistors', 'I2C address: 0x48-0x4B. 16-bit 4-channel ADC with programmable gain. Much higher resolution than the built-in 12-bit ADC. Good for precision measurements.', 'ADS1115 ADS1015 ADC analog digital converter 16-bit precision I2C'),
('ssd1306_spi', 'SSD1306 SPI OLED', 'Display', 'SPI', '{"SCK": "PA5", "MOSI": "PA7", "CS": "PA4", "DC": "PA3", "RST": "PA2"}', 'None', 'SPI OLED is faster than I2C version. DC pin selects data/command. RST pin for hardware reset. No MISO needed (display only). 0.96" or 1.3" common sizes.', 'SSD1306 OLED display SPI screen'),
('ili9341', 'ILI9341', 'TFT Display (2.4"+)', 'SPI', '{"SCK": "PA5", "MISO": "PA6", "MOSI": "PA7", "CS": "PA4", "DC": "PA3", "RST": "PA2"}', 'None', 'SPI TFT color display. 240x320 resolution. Use DMA for fast updates. Some modules include touch screen (XPT2046 on separate SPI CS). LED backlight pin needs 3.3V.', 'ILI9341 TFT LCD display color screen SPI touch');
